<text><body>
<lb n="0385b03"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0385b04"/>
<lb n="0385b05"/><head type="no">No. 1298</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0385b06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0385001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享和元年刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】永久元年寫東寺三密藏本</note>十<note n="0385002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【甲】</note><app n="0385002"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>天供儀軌<note place="inline">合兩所文為軌<note n="0385003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已出護摩軌＝也【甲】</note><app n="0385003"><lem>已出護摩軌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app></note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0385b07"/>
<lb n="0385b08"/><p>於道場八方敷茅草。或蓮荷葉或餘青草。或
<lb n="0385b09"/>塗圓壇<note n="0385004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＝分【甲】</note><app n="0385004"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">分</rdg></app>為十位。於帝釋左右置梵天地天
<lb n="0385b10"/>位。與八方而十。若道場內無置位處。即於道
<lb n="0385b11"/>場前<note n="0385005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">用＝閑【甲】</note><app n="0385005"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">閑</rdg></app>淨處別為方界。中布八方。於中央
<lb n="0385b12"/><note n="0385006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＋（作）【甲】</note><app n="0385006"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">作作</rdg></app>兩位。置梵天地天。以施十方天。食應用
<lb n="0385b13"/>雜粥。所謂梗米油麻菉豆相和煮。令極清淨。
<lb n="0385b14"/>香義盛<note n="0385007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）＋器【甲】</note><app n="0385007"><lem>器</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一器</rdg></app>中。每座先置一淨葉。巡環卒置葉
<lb n="0385b15"/>上。先以淨瓶盛水。即寫少香水於葉上以獻。
<lb n="0385b16"/>次以右手中無名二指彈少塗香。次獻一花
<lb n="0385b17"/>置之於座次獻燒香。次爐梵香。於座前獻諸
<lb n="0385b18"/>座。同此一爐。次卒一杓粥置葉上以獻。次用
<lb n="0385b19"/>小蠟燭或紙燭以獻。便&CB00961;粥上。從香水至燭。
<lb n="0385b20"/>各以本真言加持三遍。每位從水至燭獻畢。
<lb n="0385b21"/>然向。次其燭作意獻諸位。未遍已來不用令
<lb n="0385b22"/>滅。須助伴或驅使數人。各執一物以供事。若
<lb n="0385b23"/>一一自取即燭必不終事。每位於薩&CB00085;訶上
<lb n="0385b24"/>加所求願語　東方帝釋乘白象王。住五色
<lb n="0385b25"/>雲中。身作金色。右手持三股當心。左手托左
<lb n="0385b26"/>胯。左&CB00560;垂下。三天女各手持蓮花。或以盤盛
<lb n="0385b27"/>雜花等。盤<note n="0385008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔盛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0385008"><lem>盛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>青蓮花。印相者右手作拳安
<lb n="0385b28"/>腰。<note n="0385009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（右）＋左【甲】</note><app n="0385009"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">右左</rdg></app>手五指直&CB00594;相著。地水二指屈中節。
<lb n="0385b29"/>以風著火背。空屈中節。真言曰　<note n="0385010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（曩莫…賀））十七字＝（（歸命印捺囉二合耶娑&CB00085;訶））十一字【甲】</note><app n="0385010" word-count="17"><lem>曩莫三曼
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1298.0385c" n="0385c"/>
<lb n="0385c01"/>多沒馱南因捺羅耶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">歸命印捺囉二合耶娑&CB00085;訶</rdg></app>　東南方火
<lb n="0385c02"/>天乘青羊。赤肉色遍身火焰。<note n="0385011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【甲】</note><app n="0385011"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>二手一持青
<lb n="0385c03"/>竹一持軍持。<note n="0385012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左＝右【甲】</note><app n="0385012"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">右</rdg></app>二手一楊掌一持念珠。有二
<lb n="0385c04"/>天女持天花。左右置苦行仙。垂左&CB00560;<note n="0385013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蹉＝跪&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0385013"><lem>蹉</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">跪</rdg></app><note n="0385014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔右〕－【甲】</note><app n="0385014"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0385c05"/>足。印相者左手作拳安腰左。右手五指直&CB00594;
<lb n="0385c06"/>相著。屈空納著掌中。風屈中節。與娑婆訶相
<lb n="0385c07"/>招。真言曰</p><p type="dharani"><note n="0385015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（南莫…南））八字＝（（歸命））二字【甲】下同</note><app n="0385015" word-count="8"><lem>南莫三滿多沒馱南</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">歸命</rdg></app>．阿哦那<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0385c08"/>合</note>曳娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<note n="0385016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0385016"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>訶<app type="＊" source="0385016"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">南方焰摩天乘水牛。右
<lb n="0385c09"/>手執人頭幢左手仰掌。有二天女侍。二鬼
<lb n="0385c10"/>使者持刀捧戟。赤黑色垂右&CB00560;。印相者先合
<lb n="0385c11"/>掌。二地屈中節背相著。二風亦屈背著。以
<lb n="0385c12"/>大指各押風中節即成。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿
<lb n="0385c13"/>多沒馱南焰摩耶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p><p place="inline">西南方羅剎
<lb n="0385c14"/>主天乘白師子。身著甲冑。右手持刀令&CB00594;。左
<lb n="0385c15"/>手大指押中小二指。赤肉色。二天女侍左右。
<lb n="0385c16"/>二羅剎鬼。持三股戟。印相者右手作拳安腰
<lb n="0385c17"/>右。左手五指&CB00594;相著屈地水中節。以空端押
<lb n="0385c18"/>地水甲即成。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱南
<lb n="0385c19"/>乃<note n="0385017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哩＋（二合）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0385017"><lem>哩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">哩<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>底曳<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0385018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝訶【甲】</note><app n="0385018"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">西方水天住於
<lb n="0385c20"/>水中乘龜。淺綠色。右手<note n="0385019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">取＝執【甲】</note><app n="0385019"><lem>取</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">執</rdg></app>刀。左手持<note n="0385020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">龍＝&CB00559;【甲】</note><app n="0385020"><lem>龍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00559;</rdg></app>索。
<lb n="0385c21"/>冠上有五龍。四天女持妙花。印相者右手如
<lb n="0385c22"/>前。左手握拳。空勿入掌中。風即直&CB00594;。中節少
<lb n="0385c23"/>屈即成。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱南&CB00085;嚕
<lb n="0385c24"/>拏野娑&CB00085;<note n="0385021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p><p place="inline">西北方風天雲中乘&CB00538;著
<lb n="0385c25"/>甲冑。左手托胯。右手執獨股頭創。創上有緋
<lb n="0385c26"/>幡。二天女侍之。并藥叉眾印相者右手如前。
<lb n="0385c27"/>左手五指直&CB00594;相著。地水屈中節即成。真言
<lb n="0385c28"/>曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱南&CB00085;耶<note n="0385022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吠＋（微洗反）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0385022"><lem>吠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吠<note place="inline">微洗反</note></rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0385c29"/>訶</p><p place="inline">北方毘沙門天坐二鬼上。身著甲冑。左
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1298.0386a" n="0386a"/>
<lb n="0386a01"/>手掌<note n="0386001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捧＝承【甲】</note><app n="0386001"><lem>捧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">承</rdg></app>塔。右手執寶捧。身金色。二天女持
<lb n="0386a02"/>寶花等。印相者先合掌。十指內相叉。二水&CB00594;
<lb n="0386a03"/>頭相<note n="0386002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跓＝柱【甲】</note><app n="0386002"><lem>跓</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">柱</rdg></app>。二風&CB00594;微屈。左空入右掌中。押左
<lb n="0386a04"/>火甲。右空越左空背入左掌中。押右火甲。二
<lb n="0386a05"/>風與訶相招。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱南
<lb n="0386a06"/>吠室囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;拏野娑<note n="0386003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0386003"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>訶</p><p place="inline">東北方伊舍那
<lb n="0386a07"/>天舊云<note n="0386004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魔＝摩【甲】</note><app n="0386004"><lem>魔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅天。亦云大自在天。乘黃豐
<lb n="0386a08"/>牛。左手持劫<note n="0386005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＋（羅）【甲】</note><app n="0386005"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">波羅</rdg></app>杯盛血。右手持三戟創。淺
<lb n="0386a09"/>青肉色三目忿怒。二牙上出。髑髏為瓔珞。頭
<lb n="0386a10"/>冠中有二仰月。二天女持花。印相者右手作
<lb n="0386a11"/>拳安腰右。左手五指直&CB00594;相著。地水二指屈
<lb n="0386a12"/>中節。火風空三指各少相去即成。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0386a13"/><p type="dharani">南莫三漫多馱南伊舍<note n="0386006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曩曳＝那耶【甲】</note><app n="0386006"><lem>曩曳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">那耶</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0386a14"/><p>上方梵天印相者右手作拳安<note n="0386007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右腰＝腰右【甲】</note><app n="0386007"><lem>右腰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">腰右</rdg></app>。左手五
<lb n="0386a15"/>指相著&CB00594;之少屈。其高少許過肩。即成蓮花
<lb n="0386a16"/>想。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱南沒<note n="0386008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【甲】＊</note><app n="0386008"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0386a17"/><note n="0386009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶摩＝&CB05823;麼【甲】</note><app n="0386009"><lem>訶摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB05823;麼</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0386010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寧＋（尼矣反）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0386010"><lem>寧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寧<note place="inline">尼矣反</note></rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p><p place="inline">下方地天印相
<lb n="0386a18"/>者先合掌。風以下四指頭相<note n="0386011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01735;＝跓&M062403;【原】，拄【甲】</note><note n="0386011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01735;＝跓&M062403;【原】，＝拄【甲】</note><app n="0386011"><lem>&CB01735;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">跓</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">拄</rdg></app>。前方大開。
<lb n="0386a19"/>二空各著風側。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱
<lb n="0386a20"/>南畢哩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0386012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">體＋（地以反）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0386012"><lem>體</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">體<note place="inline">地以反</note></rdg></app>微曳<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p><p place="inline">日天
<lb n="0386a21"/>印相者不異前地天印。但以二空頭。各跓水
<lb n="0386a22"/>下節<note n="0386013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即成〕－【甲】</note><app n="0386013"><lem>即成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三滿多沒馱南
<lb n="0386a23"/><note n="0386014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此&CB00057;甲本作梵字&SD-CFC5;&SD-A5AB;&SD-A7D7;&SD-B065;&SD-A6A9;</note>阿<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00135;底也<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p><p place="inline">月天印相者
<lb n="0386a24"/>如前梵天印。但仰掌。中有月潔白相。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0386a25"/><p type="dharani">南莫三曼多沒馱南<note n="0386015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此&CB00057;甲本作梵字&SD-A47C;&SD-E1A6;&SD-A5F1;&SD-B065;&SD-A6A9;</note>戰捺羅<note place="inline">二合去</note>也娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0386a26"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p><p place="inline">七曜印相者先合掌十指相著。二風
<lb n="0386a27"/>與二空極相開。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三曼多沒馱
<lb n="0386a28"/>南&CB00617;<app type="＊" source="0386008"><lem>羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>醯濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>哩耶&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>跛多而
<lb n="0386a29"/><note n="0386016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偷＝渝【甲】</note><app n="0386016"><lem>偷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">渝</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0386017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">底＋（丁以反）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0386017"><lem>底</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">底<note place="inline">丁以反</note></rdg></app>羅摩耶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p><p place="inline">二十八宿
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1298.0386b" n="0386b"/>
<lb n="0386b01"/>印相者先虛心合掌。二火<note n="0386018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔外〕－【甲】</note><app n="0386018"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>相叉。二空亦相
<lb n="0386b02"/>叉。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">南莫三曼多沒馱南諾乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0386b03"/><note n="0386019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛＝但【甲】</note><app n="0386019"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">但</rdg></app>羅<app type="＊" source="0385021"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0386020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">涅＋（寧以反）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0386020"><lem>涅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">涅<note place="inline">寧以反</note></rdg></app>蘇那&CB00135;曳娑&CB00085;訶</p><p place="inline">於八方中
<lb n="0386b04"/>加兩位。上下天對。曜東宿西。諸獻並同。若別
<lb n="0386b05"/>有所願。獨用亦得。若護摩壇中。各依本方標
<lb n="0386b06"/>心令住亦設位<note place="inline">云云</note></p><p place="inline">壇中心置四臂不動尊。
<lb n="0386b07"/>青肉色。二手金剛拳。頭指小指各曲如鉤形。
<lb n="0386b08"/>安口兩角。<note n="0386021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牙相＝想&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0386021"><lem>牙相</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">想</rdg></app>如牙。右手持刀令&CB00594;。左持
<lb n="0386b09"/>索半跏右押左。坐盤石上。威焰光明遍身如
<lb n="0386b10"/>火<note place="inline">云云</note></p><p place="inline">今作圖位。但文<note n="0386022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">立＝云【甲】</note><app n="0386022"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">云</rdg></app>圓壇<note place="inline">云云</note></p><p place="inline">臨時
<lb n="0386b11"/>可作之耳。北面而可修<note n="0386023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之字次甲本有二種樣三字</note>之</p>
